       fhir:comment [ fhir:v "At least a date should be present unless this observation is a historical report.  For recording imprecise or \"fuzzy\" times (For example, a blood glucose measurement taken \"after breakfast\") use the [Timing](http://hl7.org/fhir/R4/datatypes.html#timing) datatype which allow the measurement to be tied to regular life events." ] ;
